{"tid":1064450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美大使館：用WhatsApp、留鬚、講母語 維族人隨時被關再教育營","createTime":"2019-03-16T14:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T16:46:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"894510c1f01f06b8785fdf2d25d1d61505fd154d","tid":1064450,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190316/large/1552742244_02aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190316%2Flarge%2F1552742244_02aa.jpg&h=cd71c2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院日前發表今年的人權報告，國務卿蓬佩奧批評，在侵犯人權的問題上，沒有其他國家可比得上中國，特別指超過100萬維吾爾族、哈薩克族人被關到「再教育營」。美國駐華大使館在其twitter列舉一系列可能被會被關到「再教育營」的原因，包括用WhatsApp、留鬍鬚或戴頭巾，和出國旅行等等。<br />\n<br />\n大使館的留言附帶圖片，列舉一系列「使你在中國成為打擊對象的事項」，當中包括留鬚或戴頭巾、在學校講母語、拒絕吸煙或飲酒、穿着寫有阿拉伯字母的T恤、便用WhatsApp、與官員爭執、出國旅行、舉行傳統葬禮、守齋戒或者日出前吃早餐，及到清真寺禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n留言引述蓬佩奧指，超過100萬維吾爾族、哈薩克族人被關在再教育營，旨在要消除他們的宗教和民族特徵，他更認為少數民族成為中國對人權的侵犯另一例證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59376866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376866&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=b2f60e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376866&h=1b1282f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59376866</a>"},{"pid":"05eec0758c30b8642c8718c9b9201db9c14940bd","tid":1064450,"uid":50310,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"如果用Whatsapp、出國旅遊、舉行傳統葬禮<br />\n就成為打擊對象，香港有無 一半人中招？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ab80cb469ce769bd5d47a48de585eb7b4cf07","tid":1064450,"uid":83698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"